@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ghpsei(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.62
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v2 + 0.12)) / ((tmp + 0.24 * v1 + 0.68) * (v1 + 0.50 - v0 + 0.12)))
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.47 * tmp + 0.04) / (tmp + 0.92 - v0 + 0.60)) - (0.71 - wp.exp(tmp + 0.67)))
    data[tid] = v0
